It's gotten more complicated now

1743
01:37:01,749 --> 01:37:04,585
So that our mixes
are actually taking much longer to do

1744
01:37:04,710 --> 01:37:07,921
because we have so many more tracks
that we can mix.

1745
01:37:08,130 --> 01:37:10,424
