2322
02:11:26,103 --> 02:11:28,897
Then Bob and I would start screaming
with laughter

2323
02:11:28,980 --> 02:11:32,609
and still no one...
People would be so horrified.

2324
02:11:33,110 --> 02:11:37,989
But you don't very often get to go like that.

2325
02:11:40,826 --> 02:11:43,829
Ginger was a really interesting character

2326
02:11:44,162 --> 02:11:47,499
because, of course, on the surface,
Ginger was a person

2327
02:11:47,624 --> 02:11:49,960
that just slides and "see you."

2328
02:11:50,627 --> 02:11:54,005
And we talked a lot about how

2329
02:11:54,923 --> 02:11:59,177
it's not the fact that she starts out
