2336
02:12:22,868 --> 02:12:25,871
But no, to play her, you have to play like,

2337
02:12:25,954 --> 02:12:27,956
what's her hook every time?

2338
02:12:28,206 --> 02:12:31,668
How is she going
to find a new way to win

2339
02:12:31,877 --> 02:12:34,004
in every losing situation?

