02:14:20,610 --> 02:14:24,573
STONE: There is no one more exquisite
to work for than Scorsese.

2373
02:14:24,656 --> 02:14:27,158
It just doesn't happen

2374
02:14:27,993 --> 02:14:29,911
because not only will he give you

2375
