2386
02:15:15,999 --> 02:15:18,168
And I would get calls

2387
02:15:18,835 --> 02:15:21,129
that were real up-front,

2388
02:15:21,212 --> 02:15:24,924
"I'd like to meet you, take you to lunch,"
