2389
02:15:25,008 --> 02:15:27,594
And other calls that were very

2390
02:15:29,054 --> 02:15:31,431
low-down, you know.

2391
02:15:31,973 --> 02:15:35,101
“I'll meet you on the corner,
and I'll tell you

2392
02:15:36,102 --> 02:15:37,812
"and you never saw me."

2393
02:15:38,271 --> 02:15:40,774
And people would lay some really

2394
02:15:41,524 --> 02:15:44,527
serious information on me or:

2395
02:15:46,196 --> 02:15:48,698
“I'm just going to tell you these two things."

2396
02:15:48,782 --> 02:15:52,077
