2403
02:16:19,646 --> 02:16:21,815
and some things that were so tender

2404
02:16:22,232 --> 02:16:25,819
that I got to know her.

2405
02:16:27,654 --> 02:16:31,032
And eventually,
when you play someone like that,

2406
02:16:31,574 --> 02:16:34,869
you carry them really near and dear to you

2407
02:16:35,245 --> 02:16:39,207
and some of the contacts
and relationships that I had

2408
02:16:39,290 --> 02:16:42,001
became sacred to me

2409
02:16:42,460 --> 02:16:45,588
and will always be sacred to me.

2410
02:16:46,047 --> 02:16:48,258
I felt, at a point

2411
02:16:48,717 --> 02:16:51,594
like I carried her in me.

2412
02:16:52,470 --> 02:16:53,847
ANNOUNCER: Nicholas Pileggi.

2413
02:16:53,972 --> 02:16:56,516
PILEGGI: Ginger getting so angry
at her husband

2414
02:16:57,559 --> 02:17:01,438
for all this other stuff,
