2517
02:22:40,318 --> 02:22:43,029
we found them in New Jersey, somewhere,
and Ellen Lewis...

2518
02:22:43,112 --> 02:22:45,156
So it was a very carefully...

2519
02:22:45,239 --> 02:22:48,659
That process was pretty close
to what we did in Goodfellas.

