2524
02:23:07,345 --> 02:23:08,513
You understand?

2525
02:23:08,596 --> 02:23:10,556
- I understand.
- Okay.

2526
02:23:12,058 --> 02:23:13,434
ANNQUNCER: Barbara De Fina.

2527
02:23:13,518 --> 02:23:16,187
DE FINA: Well, the violence in Casino
I think is...

2528
02:23:16,896 --> 02:23:20,817
Again, it's a true story
